---
export interface Props {
  lang: 'es' | 'en';
}
const { lang } = Astro.props;

const t = {
  es: {
    kicker: 'Sobre mí',
    title: 'De A Coruña a los escenarios del mundo.',
    body: [
      'Soy <strong>David Maestro</strong> (A Coruña, 1997). Descubrí la magia a los nueve años y a los catorce ya era mi profesión.',
      'A los dieciocho me eligieron entre trece jóvenes magos para competir en <em>Pura Magia</em>, el primer gran talent show de magia de RTVE. Llegué a la final. Después vinieron <em>Hora Punta</em>, varias colaboraciones con televisiones regionales, y otra final en <em>Got Talent España</em>.',
      'En los últimos años he sido mago residente de <em>Virgin Voyages</em>, actuando en el teatro principal de sus cruceros de lujo con aforos completos y ovaciones de pie. Sir Richard Branson vio uno de esos shows y lo describió como <em>"uno de los mejores que he visto en mi vida"</em>.',
      'Mi magia se define por la inocencia, el humor y la conexión con el público. Más que crear imposibles, hago que la gente se ría, participe y forme parte del truco desde el primer minuto.',
    ],
    signOff: '— David Maestro',
    altImage: 'David Maestro sonriendo en el escenario de un programa de televisión con luces de marquesina detrás.',
  },
  en: {
    kicker: 'About',
    title: 'From A Coruña to stages around the world.',
    body: [
      'I am <strong>David Maestro</strong> (A Coruña, 1997). I discovered magic at nine. By fourteen it became my professional career.',
      'At eighteen I was chosen from thirteen young magicians to compete on <em>Pura Magia</em>, RTVE\'s first major magic talent show. I reached the final. Then came <em>Hora Punta</em>, several regional TV collaborations, and a finalist run on <em>Spain\'s Got Talent</em>.',
      'For the past years I have been the resident magician of <em>Virgin Voyages</em>, performing in the main theatre of their luxury cruise ships to full audiences and standing ovations. Sir Richard Branson watched one of those shows and called it <em>"one of the best shows I\'ve ever seen"</em>.',
      'My magic is defined by innocence, humour and connection with the audience. More than creating impossible moments, I make people laugh, take part, and feel like part of the trick from the very first minute.',
    ],
    signOff: '— David Maestro',
    altImage: 'David Maestro smiling on stage on a television set framed by marquee lights.',
  },
}[lang];
---

<section class="about section" id="sobre-mi" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="about-grid container">
    <div class="about-media reveal">
      <div class="about-frame">
        <img
          src="/img/about.jpg"
          alt={t.altImage}
          width="1440"
          height="960"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <div class="about-frame-corner about-frame-corner-tl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="about-frame-corner about-frame-corner-br" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="kicker reveal">
        <span class="kicker-line"></span>
        <span>{t.kicker}</span>
      </div>

      <h2 id="about-title" class="type-display reveal reveal-delay-1">
        {t.title}
      </h2>

      <div class="about-body">
        {t.body.map((p, i) => (
          <p class={`type-body reveal reveal-delay-${i + 2}`} set:html={p} />
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="about-signature reveal reveal-delay-5">{t.signOff}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--surface-ink);
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 5fr 6fr;
      gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    }
  }

  .about-media {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-frame {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--surface-raised);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-frame { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
  }

  .about-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: saturate(1.05) contrast(1.08);
    transition: transform 1200ms var(--ease-out-quart);
  }

  .about-frame:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .about-frame-corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--crimson);
  }

  .about-frame-corner-tl {
    top: 12px;
    left: 12px;
    border-right: none;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .about-frame-corner-br {
    bottom: 12px;
    right: 12px;
    border-left: none;
    border-top: none;
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .kicker {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .kicker-line {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--crimson);
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.15rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-body :global(strong) {
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-body :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--crimson);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-signature {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--crimson);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
